{"tid":1448160,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"事後孔明 - 北角反送中天橋Banner都係鬼做既道具?","createTime":"2019-08-11T16:25:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T07:00:15.000Z","uid":290176,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"4bf715f52379b31e1637dc0c351513d6ccccd4db","tid":1448160,"uid":290176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:25:14.000Z","msg":"<strong>好似未見過有一次遊行都未拎不反對通知書就掛定Banner. Banner 個款同用字唔似係手足用開文宣的風格，有D生硬。張Banner 會唔會都係原先北角個伏(大圍捕)0既<span style=\"color: red;\">戲本/道具</span>? 好似做成個既定事實示威者一定要入北角，而張Banner 亦可以向中共交差證明佢地做左野? 可能我諗多左，捕風捉影.....</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20190810/_2019081016263093165.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20190810%2F_2019081016263093165.jpg&h=e87a2c85&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1564585/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E-%E8%87%AA%E7%A8%B1%E7%A6%8F%E5%BB%BA%E6%BC%A2%E5%8C%97%E8%A7%92%E5%89%AA%E7%88%9B%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E6%A9%AB%E5%B9%85-%E6%8F%9A%E8%A8%80-%E4%BD%A0%E5%80%91%E6%9C%89%E7%A8%AE%E4%BE%86%E6%8B%BF%E5%9B%9E\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1564585%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E-%25E8%2587%25AA%25E7%25A8%25B1%25E7%25A6%258F%25E5%25BB%25BA%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E5%258C%2597%25E8%25A7%2592%25E5%2589%25AA%25E7%2588%259B%25E7%25A4%25BA%25E5%25A8%2581%25E6%25A9%25AB%25E5%25B9%2585-%25E6%258F%259A%25E8%25A8%2580-%25E4%25BD%25A0%25E5%2580%2591%25E6%259C%2589%25E7%25A8%25AE%25E4%25BE%2586%25E6%258B%25BF%25E5%259B%259E&d=4tZOiqwfeINLG3hE5eaPvGAbrlwo3OpfDsLQU8t9Jac%3D&h=82f66f6f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1564585%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E-%25E8%2587%25AA%25E7%25A8%25B1%25E7%25A6%258F%25E5%25BB%25BA%25E6%25BC%25A